apertium-as-bn
==============
This is a prototype of the Assamese-Bengali language pair in Apertium.

Requirements
============
Install all the following dependencies:

* lttoolbox (http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Lttoolbox)
* apertium (http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Installation)

Installation
============
Run configure to generate a Makefile file:

$ ./configure

and then run make inside this directory.

$ make


List of files
=============
* apertium-as-bn.as.dix   	- Monolingual dictionary for Assamese
* as-bn.prob                  	- Tagger model for Assamese
* apertium-as-bn.bn.dix   	- Monolingual dictionary for Bengali
* apertium-as-bn.as-bn.t1x    	- Transfer rules for Assamese-to-Bengali translation
* apertium-as-bn.as-bn.dix    	- Bilingual dictionary
